to the editor re bush focusing on terrorism says secure us is top priority front page jan 30 president bush has issued a powerful warning to states that threaten america but let us also consider the role of more friendly countries the sept 11 hijackers and the fbi 's most wanted terrorists nearly all come from countries whose governments are aligned with the united states but who suppress their own people we must not support a system that denies our values and breeds terrorism instead let us renew and apply to these countries our successful strategy from the 1980 's of relentless support for democratic change president bush is right freedom must be our cause james radner washington jan 30 2002

